  "prompt": "What are some mind blowing iphone cases that most people don't know about?",
  "response": "When it comes to iPhone cases, there are some truly innovative and unique options out there that most people might not be aware of. Here are a few mind-blowing iPhone cases that offer more than just protection:\n\n1. **Hover Case**   \n   - Ever wanted your iPhone to float? The Hover Case integrates a gyroscope and motors to stabilize your phone mid-air. It\u2019s perfect for hands-free video calls, stable photography, or just showing off.\n\n2. **Casetagram Snack Case**   \n   - This case has a built-in compartment to store snacks! It\u2019s a quirky and fun way to carry a small stash of your favorite treats wherever you go.\n\n3. **Charcoal Purifying Case**  \n   - Designed by Airinum, this case uses activated charcoal filters to purify the air around your phone. It\u2019s perfect for people who are concerned about air quality or want a unique conversation starter.\n\n4. **NOMAD Rugged Case with MagSafe**  \n   - This case combines premium leather with rugged protection and a MagSafe-compatible design. It\u2019s sleek, durable, and functional, but not many people know about this premium option.\n\n5. **Wallet Slayer K Mount**  \n   - This case doubles as a mount for your car\u2019s air vent. It securely holds your iPhone while driving, making it a great alternative to bulky car mounts.\n\n6. **PowerSkin Battery Case**  \n   - This case not only protects your iPhone but also provides an extra 120% battery life. It\u2019s a lifesaver for heavy users who need extra power on the go.\n\n7. **KasKin Mission Belt Case**  \n   - This case includes a built-in belt clip, making it perfect for outdoor enthusiasts or anyone who wants hands-free convenience. It\u2019s durable and designed for active lifestyles.\n\n8. **Amzcase Touch ID Case**  \n   - This case features a built-in fingerprint scanner that works with Touch ID. It\u2019s a great way to add extra security to your phone without compromising on style.\n\n9. **Ztylus Camera Lens Case**  \n   - This case integrates interchangeable camera lenses (wide-angle, macro, fisheye, etc.) directly into the case. It\u2019s a must-have for photography enthusiasts.\n\n10. **Unu Ek\u00f6m Phone Case**  \n    - Made from biodegradable materials, this eco-friendly case decomposes naturally after use. It\u2019s a great choice for environmentally conscious users.\n\nThese cases go beyond the ordinary, offering unique features, functionality, and style that most people haven\u2019t even considered. If you\u2019re looking to stand out or enhance your iPhone experience, one of these might be the perfect fit!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
